title: Targets, Touches to win fantasy with Heath Cummings (Football 8/20)
description:
Will Brinson and Heath Cummings break down the latest news and notes around the NFL, including the Antonio Brown saga, the latest on Ezekiel Elliott and more before diving into the touches and targets distributions for various teams to help people win their fantasy leagues.
